-- BlackRock's bond funds see biggest monthly inflows since May 1998
-- By Jessica Toonkel
-- Thu Nov 06, 2014 04:16PM EST
-- None



Nov 6 (Reuters) - BlackRock Inc's <BLK.N> bond funds posted record monthly inflows of $5.2 billion in October, the most investors have poured into the firm's bond funds since May 1998, according to data provided to Reuters from Morningstar.

